s specific test names were provided.\\n\\n### CI Mode Steps\\n\\n1. **Download artifacts** from failed run (existing `scripts/download-e2e-artifacts.sh`)\\n2. **Identify failures** from `report.nocolor.txt` per agent (existing Step 2)\\n3. **For each failing test+agent pair, sequentially**:\\n   a. Trigger re-run: `gh workflow run e2e-isolated.yml -f agent=<agent> -f test=<TestName>`\\n   b. Wait ~5s for run to register\\n   c. Find run ID: `gh run list -w e2e-isolated.yml -L 1 --json databaseId -q '.[0].databaseId'`\\n   d. Poll until complete: loop `gh run view <id> --json status,conclusion` every 30s\\n   e. Download artifacts: `gh run download <id> --dir <rerun-dir>`\\n   f. Repeat for second re-run\\n4. **Collect results**: original failure + 2 re-run results per test\\n5. Proceed to shared analysis/classification steps\\n\\n### Shared Steps (analysis, classification, action, summary)\\n\\nLargely preserved from current skill with these enhancements:\\n\\n**Classification gains concrete re-run signals:**\\n- All runs fail with same error → strong `real-bug`\\n- Original fails, both re-runs pass → strong `flaky`\\n- Mixed results (some pass, some fail) → `flaky` (non-deterministic)\\n- Original fails, re-runs fail with *different* error → needs deeper artifact analysis\\n\\n**Cross-agent correlation** uses re-run data instead of guessing.\\n\\n**Summary table** gains a \\\"Re-run Results\\\" column showing pass/fail per run.\\n\\n## Workflow Changes (`e2e-triage.yml`)\\n\\n1. Add `actions: write` to permissions (needed for `gh workflow run`)\\n2. Increase `timeout-minutes: 30` → `timeout-minutes: 60`\\n3. Update Claude prompt to mention re-run capability and the `e2e-isolated.yml` workflow\\n4. No changes to `allowedTools` — `Bash(gh *)` already covers `gh workflow run`\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n1. **Read the updated SKILL.md** and verify both modes are clearly documented\\n2. **Local mode smoke test**: Invoke `/e2e-triage TestSomeTest --agent vogon` and verify it runs `mise run test:e2e:canary` (vogon = canary, no API cost)\\n3. **CI workflow validation**: Check that `e2e-triage.yml` has correct permissions and timeout\\n4. **Canary tests**: `mise run test:e2e:canary` should still pass (no Go code changes)\\n\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"16d62e69-2514-496b-a4b1-9ecf1b126ab7\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"f5a18f53-b820-45d5-8712-dd771912e7d9\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/e2e-triage\",\"slug\":\"agile-twirling-flask\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01UCa1b1DpJ1YuAqC4ZzNP2t\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Let me start by reading the current files that need to be modified.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":21357,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":4931,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":21357},\"output_tokens\":9,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYnUd3LncGYdoePr6QQHD\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"a168d259-6891-4007-b5bb-aa0a516fbfc6\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T20:43:11.948Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"a168d259-6891-4007-b5bb-aa0a516fbfc6\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"f5a18f53-b820-45d5-8712-dd771912e7d9\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/e2e-triage\",\"slug\":\"agile-twirling-flask\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01UCa1b1DpJ1YuAqC4ZzNP2t\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01R2fkQhksFRhJCbqm96oTCJ\",\"name\":\"ToolSearch\",\"input\":{\"query\":\"select:Read,Edit,Write,Glob,Bash\",\"max_results\":5},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":